text: Chyatay-Burzyan () is a rural locality (a village) in Bikkulovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 268 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 2.5 km from Sadovy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Chyatay-Burzyan
